name: The Rainbow News
description:
This photo was taken with a Lomo LC-A 35mm camera on the corner of 2nd Avenue and 14th Street in April, 2009. I was living in Stuyvesant Town at the time, and walked by this street corner every single day on my way to NYU. On this particular day, I had to stop dead in my tracks: the newsstands had gone technicolor. Details

name: Triangle Sunset
description:
There is a stretch of country road very close to my family's house in Canton, Ohio that I got into the habit of driving when I needed to think. I refer to it as "The Triangle," due to its configuration. This was shot one December day in 2009 as the sun was setting over the Triangle. Details
